cs.CV, cs.CR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.HC 

The paper uses deep learning algorithms to detect motorcycle helmet use from video data, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper addresses safety-critical behavioral metrics, which could be categorized under human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The paper also discusses measures to improve detection accuracy, which could be categorized under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and cryptography and security (cs.CR).
